@startuml
title ATM Control - Scenario 7: PIN Validation and Customer Options

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state WaitingForCustomerChoice
state ProcessingRequest
state Ejecting
state Confiscating
state Terminating

Idle : entry / Display Welcome

Idle --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForCustomerChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu
ValidatingPIN --> ValidatingPIN : Invalid PIN (1st Try) / Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN /\nConfiscate

WaitingForPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForCustomerChoice --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

WaitingForCustomerChoice --> ProcessingRequest : Option Selected /\nProcess Request, Display Processing

ProcessingRequest --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject
ProcessingRequest --> Terminating : Approved / Complete Transaction

Ejecting --> Terminating : Card Ejected / Display Ejected
Confiscating --> Terminating : Card Confiscated / Display Confiscated

Terminating --> Idle : After (Elapsed Time)\n[Close Down Not Requested]
@enduml
